node.text:
😳💦 Would you try this? 

Devil’s Pool is a natural pool of water that’s situated atop of Victoria Falls, renown for being among the largest waterfalls in the world. Right on the edge of this massive waterfall, a calm pool of water forms. 

This is known as the #DevilsPool #VictoriaFalls. And daring visitors can actually swim in this pool straddling the edge of Victoria Falls!

Credits: @abenafrica.

📍🇿🇲🇿🇼 #Zambia and #Zimbabwe

#thegreatplanet. Make Planet Great Again!
